# API: Implement Team Management Endpoints

## Unimplemented Endpoints
The following endpoints in `src/team_alchemy/api/routes/teams.py` must be implemented:

- `POST /teams/`: Create a new team
- `GET /teams/{team_id}`: Get team by ID
- `POST /teams/{team_id}/members/{user_id}`: Add member to team
- `GET /teams/`: List all teams

